data.description: Once entering, you will fall in love with this CHARMING 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home located in Grandridge Forest! The kitchen offers plenty of cabinets and counter space, gas stove top, double ovens and a cheery breakfast area with a lot of natural light that flows in! The living room offers a gas fireplace and nice built-in bookshelves to display all your precious treasures! Surround system throughout the house!There's a gathering room that could be used as a formal dining room! The master suite is spacious and offers double vanities, a jetted garden tub, tankless hot water, walk in shower and a huge closet! The guest rooms are nice size! Oversized laundry room with a sink, cabinets and wire racks for storage! Walk up the pretty wrought iron and wood stairs to find a bonus room/bedroom, bath and storage! This home also has a screened in back porch to sit and relax! The fenced in back yard is huge and offers plenty of room for children and animals to play! There's so much room for entertaining guests! Outside also offers a fire pit, storage building and a sprinkler system! This home has so much to offer!
